software compilation from source

1. dependencies / third party software
  compiler - gcc / gfortran etc.
  software - tcl, tk, freetype etc

2. environment var definition
  check SOFTWARE_DIR, may exit env.sh
  add source env.sh to ~/.bashrc

3. compilation
  a-- cmake .
  b-- ./configure
  c-- autoconf
  
4. install
  copy lib file, header file, bin file etc to /usr/local/lib
  
5. setup ldconf
  let the bin file (exe file) program know the lib location
 
 
example:

  OpenFOAM
  
  OpenCascade
  
  Qt
  
  OpenSceneGraph
  
  MeshKit
